  25 Nov 2004; Simone Gotti <motaboy@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  +files/arson-0.9.8_beta2-configure-arts.patch, arson-0.9.8_beta2.ebuild:
  Added a patch to the configure script to honor the arts USE flag. Fixes bug
  #71816.

  06 Oct 2004; Lars Weiler <pylon@gentoo.org> arson-0.9.8_beta2.ebuild:
  Changed dependency from app-cdr/cdrtools to virtual/cdrtools. This resolves
  bug #66518.

